organization (the "User") obtaining a copy of this software and
associated documentation files (the "Software"), to use, copy, modify,
merge, distribute, and/or sell copies of the Software, subject to the
following conditions:

1. The above copyright notice and this permission notice shall be
   included in all copies or modified versions of the Software.

2. The User is one of the following:
   a. An individual person, laboring for themselves
   b. A non-profit organization
   c. An educational institution
   d. An organization that seeks shared ownership among all of its
      members, and does not concentrate compensation in the hands of a
      few (e.g. combensation differentials of 10x or less)
   e. An organization with an explicitly anti-capitalist mission

3. If the User is an organization with owners, combensation differentials
   must be reasonable (suggested: no greater than 10:1 between highest
   and lowest paid workers).

